{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/what-is-jaas/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Funny Eagle","author":"Jason Yang"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"5f6c072a-1a73-5b12-b956-52cc48452253","excerpt":"JAAS（Java Authentication and Authorization Service）配置是Java中用于实现身份验证和授权的标准机制，在Kafka客户端中主要用于配置安全认证信息（…","html":"<p>JAAS（Java Authentication and Authorization Service）配置是Java中用于实现身份验证和授权的标准机制，在Kafka客户端中主要用于配置安全认证信息（如用户名、密码）。以下是关于JAAS配置的详细说明：</p>\n<h3 id=\"1-什么是jaas\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E6%98%AFjaas\" aria-label=\"1 什么是jaas permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>1. 什么是JAAS？</strong></h3>\n<p>JAAS是Java平台提供的安全框架，允许应用程序：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>验证用户身份</strong>（Authentication）：确认用户是谁。</li>\n<li><strong>授权访问资源</strong>（Authorization）：决定用户可以做什么。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>在Kafka中，JAAS配置主要用于存储认证所需的凭证（如用户名和密码），并指定使用的认证机制（如SCRAM、PLAIN、GSSAPI等）。</p>\n<h3 id=\"2-kafka中的jaas配置格式\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-kafka%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84jaas%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%A0%BC%E5%BC%8F\" aria-label=\"2 kafka中的jaas配置格式 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>2. Kafka中的JAAS配置格式</strong></h3>\n<p>JAAS配置通常以字符串形式嵌入到Kafka客户端的配置中，格式为：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\">props<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">put</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"sasl.jaas.config\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"LoginModuleClassName required option1=value1 option2=value2;\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>LoginModuleClassName</strong>：指定使用的登录模块类，例如：\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">org.apache.kafka.common.security.plain.PlainLoginModule</code>（PLAIN机制）</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">org.apache.kafka.common.security.scram.ScramLoginModule</code>（SCRAM机制）</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">com.sun.security.auth.module.Krb5LoginModule</code>（Kerberos机制）</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>required</strong>：表示该登录模块是必需的。</li>\n<li><strong>option</strong>：配置选项，如<code class=\"language-text\">username</code>、<code class=\"language-text\">password</code>等。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"3-常见jaas配置示例\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81jaas%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B\" aria-label=\"3 常见jaas配置示例 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>3. 常见JAAS配置示例</strong></h3>\n<h4 id=\"-plain机制用户名密码\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-plain%E6%9C%BA%E5%88%B6%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E5%90%8D%E5%AF%86%E7%A0%81\" aria-label=\" plain机制用户名密码 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>① PLAIN机制（用户名+密码）</strong></h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\">props<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">put</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"sasl.jaas.config\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> \n    <span class=\"token string\">\"org.apache.kafka.common.security.plain.PlainLoginModule required \"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"username=\\\"your_username\\\" \"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"password=\\\"your_password\\\";\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"-scram-sha-256512机制\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-scram-sha-256512%E6%9C%BA%E5%88%B6\" aria-label=\" scram sha 256512机制 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>② SCRAM-SHA-256/512机制</strong></h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\">props<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">put</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"sasl.jaas.config\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> \n    <span class=\"token string\">\"org.apache.kafka.common.security.scram.ScramLoginModule required \"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"username=\\\"your_username\\\" \"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"password=\\\"your_password\\\";\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"-kerberos机制gssapi\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-kerberos%E6%9C%BA%E5%88%B6gssapi\" aria-label=\" kerberos机制gssapi permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>③ Kerberos机制（GSSAPI）</strong></h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\">props<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">put</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"sasl.jaas.config\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> \n    <span class=\"token string\">\"com.sun.security.auth.module.Krb5LoginModule required \"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"useKeyTab=true \"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"storeKey=true \"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"keyTab=\\\"/path/to/your/keytab\\\" \"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"principal=\\\"your_principal@YOUR.REALM\\\";\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"4-在kafka客户端中配置jaas\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#4-%E5%9C%A8kafka%E5%AE%A2%E6%88%B7%E7%AB%AF%E4%B8%AD%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEjaas\" aria-label=\"4 在kafka客户端中配置jaas permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>4. 在Kafka客户端中配置JAAS</strong></h3>\n<h4 id=\"方式一代码中直接配置推荐\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E4%B8%80%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E4%B8%AD%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%8E%A8%E8%8D%90\" aria-label=\"方式一代码中直接配置推荐 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>方式一：代码中直接配置（推荐）</strong></h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token class-name\">Properties</span> props <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Properties</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nprops<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">put</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"sasl.jaas.config\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">format</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"org.apache.kafka.common.security.scram.ScramLoginModule required \"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"username=\\\"%s\\\" password=\\\"%s\\\";\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"your_username\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"your_password\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"方式二通过jaas配置文件\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E4%BA%8C%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87jaas%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6\" aria-label=\"方式二通过jaas配置文件 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>方式二：通过JAAS配置文件</strong></h4>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>创建<code class=\"language-text\">kafka_client_jaas.conf</code>文件：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"properties\"><pre class=\"language-properties\"><code class=\"language-properties\"><span class=\"token key attr-name\">KafkaClient</span> <span class=\"token value attr-value\">{</span>\n<span class=\"token key attr-name\">    org.apache.kafka.common.security.scram.ScramLoginModule</span> <span class=\"token value attr-value\">required</span>\n<span class=\"token key attr-name\">    username</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token value attr-value\">\"your_username\"</span>\n<span class=\"token key attr-name\">    password</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token value attr-value\">\"your_password\";</span>\n};</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>在Java启动时指定配置文件路径：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">java</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-Djava.security.auth.login.config</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>/path/to/kafka_client_jaas.conf <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-jar</span> your-app.jar</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>在代码中简化配置：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\">props<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">put</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"sasl.jaas.config\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"KafkaClient\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"5-注意事项\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#5-%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E4%BA%8B%E9%A1%B9\" aria-label=\"5 注意事项 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>5. 注意事项</strong></h3>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p><strong>安全性</strong>：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>密码不应硬编码在代码中，建议通过环境变量或配置中心获取。</li>\n<li>生产环境推荐使用SASL_SSL协议（同时启用认证和加密）。</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>与其他配置的配合</strong>：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">sasl.mechanism</code>必须与JAAS配置中的登录模块匹配（如SCRAM-SHA-256对应<code class=\"language-text\">ScramLoginModule</code>）。</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">security.protocol</code>指定传输协议（如SASL_PLAINTEXT或SASL_SSL）。</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>调试技巧</strong>：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>添加系统属性<code class=\"language-text\">-Djava.security.debug=loginconfig,jaas</code>可查看JAAS详细调试信息。</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"6-总结\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#6-%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93\" aria-label=\"6 总结 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>6. 总结</strong></h3>\n<p>JAAS配置是Kafka客户端实现安全认证的核心机制，通过指定登录模块和凭证信息，确保客户端能够合法访问Kafka集群。不同的认证机制（如PLAIN、SCRAM、Kerberos）对应不同的JAAS配置格式，需根据实际环境选择合适的配置方式。</p>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#1-%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E6%98%AFjaas\"><strong>1. 什么是JAAS？</strong></a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#2-kafka%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84jaas%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%A0%BC%E5%BC%8F\"><strong>2. Kafka中的JAAS配置格式</strong></a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#3-%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81jaas%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B\"><strong>3. 常见JAAS配置示例</strong></a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#-plain%E6%9C%BA%E5%88%B6%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E5%90%8D%E5%AF%86%E7%A0%81\"><strong>① PLAIN机制（用户名+密码）</strong></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#-scram-sha-256512%E6%9C%BA%E5%88%B6\"><strong>② SCRAM-SHA-256/512机制</strong></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#-kerberos%E6%9C%BA%E5%88%B6gssapi\"><strong>③ Kerberos机制（GSSAPI）</strong></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#4-%E5%9C%A8kafka%E5%AE%A2%E6%88%B7%E7%AB%AF%E4%B8%AD%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEjaas\"><strong>4. 在Kafka客户端中配置JAAS</strong></a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E4%B8%80%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E4%B8%AD%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%8E%A8%E8%8D%90\"><strong>方式一：代码中直接配置（推荐）</strong></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E4%BA%8C%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87jaas%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6\"><strong>方式二：通过JAAS配置文件</strong></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#5-%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E4%BA%8B%E9%A1%B9\"><strong>5. 注意事项</strong></a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#6-%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93\"><strong>6. 总结</strong></a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"JAAS是什么","tags":["coding"],"description":"JAAS配置是Kafka客户端实现安全认证的核心机制，通过指定登录模块和凭证信息，确保客户端能够合法访问Kafka集群。不同的认证机制（如PLAIN、SCRAM、Kerberos）对应不同的JAAS配置格式，需根据实际环境选择合适的配置方式。","date":"2025-07-02"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/what-is-jaas","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/goaccess-show-cn-and-location"},"frontmatter":{"title":"goaccess设置为中文报告并显示访客地理位置","tags":["coding"],"slug":"/goaccess-show-cn-and-location"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/wscat"},"frontmatter":{"title":"使用wscat进行WebSocket通信测试","tags":["coding"],"slug":"/wscat"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["2052298874"],"slicesMap":{}}